{"tid":1148072,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"漫畫「孔雀王」作者荻野真逝世，享年59歲","createTime":"2019-05-10T08:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T17:46:31.000Z","uid":183666,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f88e40255f541f5e8c65352d7c9180c4299d8d1","tid":1148072,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E6FrSH0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE6FrSH0.png&h=811121a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nアニメ化・実写化もされた漫画『孔雀王』などで知られる漫画家の荻野真（おぎの・まこと）さんが、4月29日に腎不全のため死去した。享年59。同作が連載された『ヤングジャンプ』の公式サイトで10日、発表された。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20190510-00000359-oric-ent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Fhl%3Fa%3D20190510-00000359-oric-ent&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=3b616e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20190510-00000359-oric-ent</a>"},{"pid":"50eadef6171b7b0c81f16f03dbcfba4ed558d50b","tid":1148072,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:55:21.000Z","msg":"日本漫畫《孔雀王》作者荻野真今傳出 4 月 29 日因腎衰竭在家中過世，享年 59 歲。荻野真先前就曾在官方網站向書迷報告住院近況，並且定期至醫院接受治療，沒想到還是不幸過世。<br />\n<br />\n比較年輕的朋友可能對荻野真以及他的成名作品《孔雀王》不是很清楚，荻野真當年在漫畫大賞中以《孔雀王》故事獲獎出道，就在「週刊 YoungJump」以《孔雀王》連載。他的故事算是比較罕見的宗教神怪故事，尤其講述的是日本的密教，許多人對於「高野」、「裏高野」，「臨兵鬥者皆陣列在前」等等日本密教的相關知識都是從這部漫畫而來的。<br />\n<br />\n不過荻野真之後推出的漫畫相對的話題以及好評度都沒有《孔雀王》的第一部來得高，像是《夜叉鴨》、《ALGO！》、《小類人》等等漫畫，表現只能說平平。而荻野真也有推出孔雀王系列後來的《退魔聖傳》、《曲神記》等等，但是故事上也沒有第一部來得那麼完整而精彩。"},{"pid":"117b38cb164725feed8c823e585b9295e3a805e8","tid":1148072,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"過唔到平成"},{"pid":"0eda7b653004404ded9dc9fa0f6db7205cabf11a","tid":1148072,"uid":202137,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"D畫越畫退步,第一套D女J死人,之後D作品骨架都畫到變哂型,D女除哂衫似十足成隻哥布林,睇到鳩都縮"},{"pid":"e5c176193c630e7065533347a13699989906e08b","tid":1148072,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"屌你咩<br />\n由十歲開始睇<br />\n由退魔聖傳<br />\n再到魔界考察傳<br />\n等咗十鳩幾年出<br />\n曲神又斷尾<br />\n孔雀皇起義又斷<br />\n孔雀皇戰國轉生又斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab193170ec6c3a79f695547f2484d7b13b584591","tid":1148072,"uid":56212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"噢&hellip;中學時已睇嘅 孔雀王&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n真係好好睇&hellip;而家間唔中都有番睇吓"},{"pid":"565c8ca783a4957c6bbeb2486bff2d1be34454c5","tid":1148072,"uid":171845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2beee924349007a382b07c01e5fbf77b3a7116a6","tid":1148072,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"《孔雀王》漫畫家荻野真腎衰竭離世<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190510/photo/bkn-20190510152531967-0510_00862_001_01b.jpg?20190510170403\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190510%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190510152531967-0510_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20190510170403&h=14bf99d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本經典漫畫《孔雀王》原作者荻野真，證實於4月29日因腎衰竭離世，享年59歲，其近親於本月8日已為他低調舉殯，曾連載《孔雀王》的漫畫雜誌《Young Jump》於官網公布荻野的死訊。<br />\n<br />\n荻野真於1985年以《孔雀王》於《Young Jump》上連載出道，筆下作品包括有《夜叉鴉》、《電腦啟示錄》等。《孔雀王》於1988年曾改編成港日合作的真人版電影，由元彪、葉蘊儀、王小鳳、三上博史等演出，翌年改名《孔雀王子》在香港上映，後來再開拍續集《阿修羅》，男星阿部寬亦有份演出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190510/bkn-20190510152531967-0510_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190510%2Fbkn-20190510152531967-0510_00862_001.html&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=6db6ae4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190510/bkn-20190510152531967-0510_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7a984fc99a44f8b3c4fd4cf990ad418fe88349cd","tid":1148072,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"第一部好好睇, 又密宗, 又滿天神佛, 仲有佢家姐原來係 big boss, 少少咸, 多多趣 ! 之後退魔聖傳好似作畫仲差左 ! <br />\nr.i.p !"},{"pid":"e012222645df3a66ec8bbadb09429aa32c850904","tid":1148072,"uid":183666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKFodkc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKFodkc.jpg&h=5f8423be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8702fbec72c0614371f87a62a3e2af6a558ca70f","tid":1148072,"uid":56212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"自細都鍾意孔雀王，帳號名都係裏面其中一個角色"}]}